Residential Intercom System Market Size, Share, and Forecast Analysis
The residential intercom system market has demonstrated consistent growth over the past decade, driven by escalating demand for enhanced security, smart home integration, and user convenience. As of the latest available data, the global market valuation stands at approximately USD 4.2 billion in 2023, reflecting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of around 7.2% over the previous five years. This upward trajectory underscores the increasing adoption of interconnected home communication solutions across developed and emerging economies.

